title: Dusted - When We Were Young (2000).rar
description:
&quot;This is Rollo`s (from Faithless) solo record and it`s brilliant. It`s got choirboys in it. Madness. It`s going to be a big hit.&quot; PAUL OAKENFOLD

&quot;...pure tear jerking Ibiza sunset material - a proper album you can listen to and enjoy from the beginnig to end, again and again.&quot; DJ (10/10)

&quot;There`s no doubting Rollo`s musical excellence - imagine the lushness of Massive Attack`s Teardrops times 10.&quot; Q MAGAZINE
